snippet.title: Halo 3 E3 2007 Trailer
snippet.description: While September is still off in the distance, right now, a small part of the wait is over. Here is the Halo 3 E3 Trailer, a visual and aural presentation destined to eradicate your senses and whip you into a frenzy.
